The second one had a mammoth that thought she was an opossum and there was a giant ice wall around.... Wherever it is that they were.... Which came out of nowhere and wasn't there in the first movie. Then they had dinosaurs underground. Physically disproportionate dinosaurs. Then... Geez, I still have trouble even registering the fourth one in my brain.
